Package dev.morphia.geo

Class MultiPoint

java.lang.Object
dev.morphia.geo.MultiPoint
All Implemented Interfaces:
Geometry
@Deprecated(since="2.0", forRemoval=true) public class MultiPoint extends Object implements Geometry
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
use the driver-provided types instead
This class represents a series of points, which will saved into MongoDB as per the GeoJSON specification.

The factory for creating a MultiPoint is the GeoJson.multiPoint method.

See Also:
